results.raw: Fatal Shooting Investigation at 7th St E & Mounds Blvd, Saint Paul, Minnesota, 55106
results.rawLocation: 7th St E & Mounds Blvd, Saint Paul, Minnesota, 55106
results.title: Fatal Shooting Investigation

-MiJoI_kbbBHi7ixQeTq.text: Citizen user sumoshouldntbeher shows a large police presence at an incident.

-MiK26Msox4bCSNSRW10.text: The address reported for this incident has changed to 7th St E & Mounds Blvd.

-MiK26V6sXL0oGFpQXWn.text: According to a tweet from the St Paul Police Department, police are investigating the fatal shooting that occurred earlier in the evening. No suspect information is available.

-MiKTBX04FvARkrr2eS9.text: According to a press release from the St Paul Police Department, police received a 911 call for shots fired around 8:45 pm. Officers responded to the scene at 7 St E and Mounds Blvd where theyfound a man believed to be in his late teensinside a vehicle. He was unconscious, but breathingand suffering from gunshot wounds. Police rendered aid to the man while they secured the scene. EMS transported the man to a local hospital where he was pronounced deceased a short time later. Investigators from the homicide unit are working to locate possible witnesses who can help them identify the person or people responsible for the death. Members of the forensic services unit will process the scene and the area for evidence, and the video management unit will work to locate surveillancevideo. Preliminary information indicates this shooting may be connected to a road rage incident, however its unclear how the victim was involved. No arrests have been made. Anyone with information about this shooting is asked to call the homicide unit at 651-266-5650.
